SUMMARY:Week without driving
DESCRIPTION:Dallas Week Without Driving Partner Organizations:\nCo-hosts: Dallas Bicycle Coalition\, Better Block\nPartners: Feonix Mobility\, Dallas Area Transit Alliance\, DFW Urbanistas\, Dallas Youth Commission\, Dallas Disability Commission\, and Dallas Neighbors for Housing\nHow can you support?\nSign up on the national site. Select elected official\, transportation official\, individual\, or your appropriate role. \nhttps://weekwithoutdriving.org/join/\nParticipate by replacing as many car trips as possible with walking\, transit\, or biking. One trip or one day is a success. A perfect week is not the goal!\nTag us on social media @betterblock and @dallasbicyclecoalition with the hashtag #WeekWithoutDriving and #WeekWithoutDrivingDallas\nJoin us for Happy Hour on Friday\, October 4 from 5-7 at Westlake Brewing!\n
X-ORGANIZING-GROUP:Dallas Bicycle Coalition
X-TEAMUP-WHO:Dallas Bicycle Coalition
X-EVENT-TYPE:social_gathering
X-REJECTED:false
CREATED:20241011T015818Z
LAST-MODIFIED:00010101T000000Z
