SUMMARY:Bike to City Hall
DESCRIPTION:In conjunction with CMs Moreno\, Ridley\, and Deputy Mayor Pro Tem Bazaldua\, CM West is hosting the 2024 Bike to City Hall event on Wednesday October 23rd. The first event was held in 2011 and it has been an annual tradition since then to promote cycling as an innovative\, viable means of affordable transportation. This year\, CM West will be honoring iBike Rosemont!\nSchedule:\nBetween 7:30AM – 7:45AM\, Councilmembers and other bicyclists will meet at Pacific Plaza\, 401 N Harwood.\n7:45AM – Group photo\n8:00AM\, all bicyclists\, escorted by DPD’s bike squad\, ride out to City Hall Plaza (route is being reviewed).\nAt 8:20AM\, there will be a press event at City Hall Plaza\n
LOCATION:Pacific Plaza 401 N Harwood St, Dallas, TX 75215, USA
X-ORGANIZING-GROUP:Dallas Bicycle Coalition
X-TEAMUP-WHO:Dallas Bicycle Coalition
X-EVENT-TYPE:social_gathering
X-REJECTED:false
