DTSTAMP:20260217T204255Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Chicago:20250202T120000
DTEND;TZID=America/Chicago:20250202T150000
SUMMARY:Tweed Ride Dallas
DESCRIPTION:The Dallas Tweed Ride is officially this Sunday\, February 2nd starting at the grassy knoll in downtown Dallas. Dress in your favorite 1920's attire and bicycle down to meet us at noon. We'll roll out at 12:30 p.m. and circle around downtown with a few historic stops along the way\, and then on to the Bishop Arts District for games\, live jazz music with the \n@bishopavenuehotsix\n and more at Jaquval Brewpub!\n\nSee more on IG at \n@jaquval\n.\n
LOCATION:The Grassy Knoll 411 Elm St, Dallas, TX 75202
