SUMMARY:DBC Coffee Social (Social Ride to Follow)
DESCRIPTION:Join the Dallas Bicycle Coalition board for our first event of the year! We'll be hanging out at The Meteor Cafe from 10-11:30a for morning coffee and good conversation. Learn about our 2025 goals\, sign up to get involved\, and give input on our advocacy priorities for the year. \nOptionally\, join the Hangover Riders for a 10-12 mile social ride\, leaving from The Meteor at 11:30.\nRSVP: https://actionnetwork.org/events/february-coffee-social/\n
