UID:dbc_4f5fd653-d0b6-4b96-88a3-53c7205872fd
DTSTAMP:20260217T204255Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Chicago:20250308T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Chicago:20250308T210000
SUMMARY:Bike Story Night Dallas!
DESCRIPTION:Bike Story Night is Coming to Dallas!\nJoin us for an unforgettable evening where we come together to share the magic of storytelling\, reconnect with old bike friends\, and make new connections. We also like to shine a spotlight on different local bike non-profits at each event.\nAt Bike Story Night\, our mission is to empower individuals to share their unique stories with the community\, both in-person and online. These events serve as a platform for diverse voices\, celebrating the intersection of storytelling and the joy of cycling.\nGet tickets (suggested donation $10-$20)\n\nPS don't miss the social ride beforehand!\nRide Leader: Jaime Ramirez from Hangover Riders\n📍Starting Point: 5PM Dallas Farmers Market - 920 S Harwood St\nROLL OUT 5:30\n🎤Mid Stop: 6:15 - 9PM ~ 🎤🚲Bike Story Night at 🍻Four Corners Brewing Co.\n📍Ending: Back at the Start\nHow many miles total? (6miles) What's your average pace? 10-12 mph\n
LOCATION:Four Corners Brewery 1311 S Ervay St. Dallas, TX 75215
