SUMMARY:Coombs Creek Trail Extension Celebration
DESCRIPTION:Join Chad West\, Dallas City Council District 1\, and JR Huerta\, Dallas Park and Recreation Board District 1\, and experience Dallas’ newest trail extension. Bring your bicycles to Moss Park for the opening celebration\, then cycle 4 miles to the new Coombs Creek Trail Bridge by Beckley Avenue for the ribbon-cutting. After the ceremony\, attendees are welcome to return home or continue informal celebrations at Chip’s Old Fashioned Hamburgers\, 1605 N. Beckley Avenue.\n
LOCATION:Moss Park 2600 Sunset Avenue Dallas, TX 75211
