SUMMARY:Pop-up Ride with Dallas Bike Ride, Hangover Riders, Trek & Downtown Dallas
DESCRIPTION:Sign up for free: https://www.eventbrite.com/e/pop-up-ride-with-dallas-bike-ride-hangover-riders-trek-downtown-dallas-tickets-1291300637969\nKick off the Spring with a bike ride to celebrate Dallas’s artistry!\nThis April 13th\, Dallas Bike Ride is partnering with Hangover Riders Bike Club\, TREK Bicycles\, and Downtown Dallas to promote our very first Pop-Up Ride!\nThis is an open-road\, approachable social ride recommended for riders comfortable sharing the road with automotive vehicles as it includes roads with mild to heavy traffic.\nWe invite riders to meet at the Farmers Market at 10 am to get you ready to roll. Please listen carefully to the road and safety guidelines and bring your helmet and bike in good riding conditions. Arrive around 9:30 am to allow yourself enough time to park and gear up.\nThe ride ends at the Downtown Dallas Arts & Music Festival\, where riders are welcome to a program full of fun activities.\n\n
LOCATION:Dallas Farmers Market 920 S Harwood St, Dallas, TX 75201, USA
