SUMMARY:DBC Spring 2025 General Meeting
DESCRIPTION:RSVP so we know to expect you: https://actionnetwork.org/events/dbc-spring-2025-general-meeting\n\nEvery spring and fall\, Dallas Bicycle Coalition organizes a general meeting so bike advocates in Dallas have the opportunity to gather and hear from leaders working to make streets safer\, biking a more popular choice\, and alternatives to driving more accessible. RSVP so we know to expect you!\n\n\nDetails:\nThursday\, April 17 at 7pm\nFour Corners Brewing Company\n\nSpeakers:\nCatherine Richardson\, North Central Texas Council of Governments\n\nRose Thompson\, Black Women Who\n\nTameca Harris\, Bike Friendly South Dallas\n
