SUMMARY:Oak Cliff Book Crawl Bike Crawl (with Bike Friendly Oak Cliff)
DESCRIPTION:Join DBC and Bike Friendly Oak Cliff for a bike crawl through Oak Cliff to support the 3rd annual Oak Cliff Book Crawl. This will be a social pace ride about 10 miles long. Bring water and remember to support your local Oak Cliff book stores along the way!\n\nDetails:\nMeet at Whose Books at 11am\nRoute- Whose Books -> Lucky Dog -> PAC DAllas ->Back to Bishop Arts for lunch\nLunch around 1pm at Jaquval/Trades\n\nReserve your spot for the Book Crawl here: \nhttps://www.eventbrite.com/e/3rd-annual-oak-cliff-book-crawl-tickets-1294938589179\n
