SUMMARY:Intro to Bikepacking w/ Backyard Bikepacking DFW (Cedar Hill SP)
DESCRIPTION:We are very excited to announce our Spring Bikepacking Calendar!\n\n🪨 Erwin 2 Eisenhower\nDate: Apr 19 & 20\nStart: Erwin Park\nEnd: Eisenhower SP\n\n📑 Intro to Bikepacking\nDate: May 3 & 4\nStart: Dallas (White Rock Alehouse)\nEnd: Cedar Hill SP\n\n🐝 Waxahachie 2 Bee Mountain\nDate: May 31 & June 1\nStart: Waxahachie (Location TBD)\nEnd: Bee Mountain Resort\n\nMore details and registration links for trips will be shared closer to the event dates. All attendees must register.\n``````````````````````````````````````````````````\nThis May\, Backyard Bikepacking DFW is hosting our second “Intro to Bikepacking” event. This will be a great opportunity to try out bikepacking without the hassle of planning a route\, finding a crew\, or leaving your backyard.\n\nWe will be heading from White Rock Lake to Cedar Hill State Park (50 mile round trip) and camping overnight. Once at the campsite\, there will be opportunities for swimming\, hiking\, fishing\, and birdwatching. Our campsites will have water\, electricity\, and restrooms to make this a comfortable camping experience.\n\nWhat your entry gets you:\n\n⛺ Park entry and campsite spot\n📋 Pre-trip prep class (date TBD)\n👨‍🔧 Ride support from the Backyard Bikepacking team\n\nWe truly want first-timers to feel welcome\, so if you have any questions\, concerns\, or requests\, please send us an email (backyard.bikepacking.dfw@gmail.com).\nFollow \nbackyard.bikepacking.dfw\n on IG for more information.\n
LOCATION:Cedar Hill State Park
X-ORGANIZING-GROUP:Dallas Bicycle Coalition
X-TEAMUP-WHO:Dallas Bicycle Coalition
