SUMMARY:Dallas Bike Ride: Dallas’s only car-free social ride is back!
DESCRIPTION:Dallas’s only car-free social ride is back!\nDallas Bike Ride is a celebration on two wheels! Join us for a fun\, social ride- completely car-free- and cruise at your own pace past our city’s most iconic sights — perfect for first-timers and avid cyclists alike!\nRegister at \nregister.dallasbikeride.com\n\nDallas Bicycle Coalition is a proud community partner of Dallas Bike Ride. Get 15% off your registration with code "DALLASLOVESBIKES". Learn more here:\n https://dallasbikeride.com/community-impact/\n\nRide Information. See more at \nhttps://dallasbikeride.com/ride-information/\nSaturday\, May 17\n6:00 AM Corrals Open\n7:45 AM Corrals Close\n8:00 AM Ride Begins\n8:30 AM Finish Festival Begins\n
LOCATION:1500 Marilla St, Dallas, TX 75201
