SUMMARY:Grand Avenue Study Public Meeting
DESCRIPTION:Learn more and sign up for updates: \nwww.publicinput.com/grandavenue\n\nWhat improvements would you like to see on Grand Avenue between the “3G” Intersection and Interstate 30? Join NCTCOG for a public meeting and share your thoughts. Following public feedback on early planning and design concepts\, the project team has developed a series of draft recommendations for each segment in the corridor. These recommendations combine roadway\, safety\, and bicycle/pedestrian improvements\, as well as improvements to school drop off/pick up areas. Members of the community will be invited to comment on the draft recommendations.\n
LOCATION:Mt. Auburn Elementary School: 6012 E. Grand Avenue, Dallas, TX 75223
