SUMMARY:Katy Trail 5k (DBC Bike Valet)
DESCRIPTION:Join us for the Katy 5K\, a unique course that takes you through some of the most beautiful parts of Dallas. DBC bike valet provided!\nJoin us for the Katy 5K\, a unique course that takes you through some of the most beautiful parts of Dallas\, including Turtle Creek\, the Uptown streets of Dallas\, and the beautiful Katy Trail. Post race\, celebrate with us at the Picnic Party with live entertainment by DJ EJ: The Official DJ for the Dallas Cowboys\, two complimentary Michelob ULTRA beverages (21 & over)\, free food from over 30 local eateries\, sponsor swag\, and selfie stations throughout the Katy 5K Picnic Party. It is sure to be an unforgettable experience! DBC Bike Valet provided! Volunteers needed for the valet if you aren't running.\nRegister: https://katytraildallas.org/5k/\nSign up to volunteer for the \nbike valet.\n (Edit - rolls are filled! Thank you)\n
LOCATION:Reverchon Park (3505 Maple Ave., Dallas, TX 75219)
