SUMMARY:Hangover Riders 10 Year Anniversary Ride
DESCRIPTION:Hop on your bike in style\, decked out in your snazziest Hawaiian shirt collection! Our biking adventure starts at Dallas Farmers Market\, cruising to Four Corners for a fiesta of tacos and cold brews. Come out and celebrate our 10th Anniversary party. We will have a DJ.\n\nPacheco Taco N Burger will be selling Tacos and Burgers. Let’s brighten up the streets with our colorful shirts!\n\nThis ride will cover 12-15 miles\, cruising leisurely 10-12 mph. Stay tuned for the route details\, which will be coming soon.\n\n‼️Get ready to pedal out at 1pm SHARP from Farmers Market. Please arrive early\, and let’s hit the road!‼️\n
