SUMMARY:The Loop Dallas Hi-Line Trail Experience (DBC Social Ride Before)
DESCRIPTION:*A DBC ride\, lead by Miso Ryu\, leaves from The Meteor at 6pm. There will be a stop to enjoy the Hi-Line Trail Experience\, and then the ride will continue.\n\nHi-Line Trail Experience Details:\nWhen: Tuesday\, October 14\, 2025\, 5:30 PM – 7:30 PM \nWhere: The Hi Line Connector \nAddress: Hi Line Drive between Slocum St. and Oak Lawn Ave.\nYou’re invited to a special evening celebrating the Hi Line Connector—one of the newest completed connections in The Loop Dallas trail system. We hope you’ll join us to experience some fun activation on the trail\, as we shine a spotlight on our city’s creative spirit and exciting milestones in our journey to connect Dallas to Dallas. Come enjoy the trail experiences: we’ll have an artist talk from the incredible muralists (@mariellguzman\, @thesamlao\, @marpohl\, @youcancallmealec @wheron\, @hatziel) a @neighborhoodsupply customized hat-making bar\, a live band and @djsober\, @wheels_of_giving\, a @ruthiesforgood food truck\, @pullthroughcoffeebar beverages...and more\n
LOCATION:Event is at The Hi Line Connector, Social Ride meets at The Meteor Cafe
