DTEND;TZID=America/Chicago:20251020T170000
SUMMARY:Pedal to the Park
DESCRIPTION:Join City Council Members for a community bike ride!\nPedal to the Park is the revamped Bike to City Hall! The first event was held in 2011 and it has been an annual tradition since then to promote cycling as an innovative\, viable means of affordable transportation.\n\nAgenda:\n4:00 - gather at City Hall and bike to Klyde Warren\n4:20 - press conference and photos at Klyde Warren Park\n4:45- bike and arrive to Dallas Farmers Market for refreshments by 5pm\n\n
LOCATION:Dallas City Hall
