UID:TU1961746570
DTSTAMP:20260217T204255Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Chicago:20251024T130000
DTEND;TZID=America/Chicago:20251024T150000
SUMMARY:CNU Walking Tour | Canals at Grand Park and Frisco Square (Discover how Arcadia’s Canals at Frisco Square brings New Urbanism to life on a guided CNU walking tour.)
DESCRIPTION:Who: Discover how Arcadia’s Canals at Frisco Square brings New Urbanism to life on a guided CNU walking tour.\n\nDiscover how Arcadia’s Canals at Frisco Square brings New Urbanism to life on a guided CNU walking tour.CNU Walking Tour | Canals at Grand Park and Frisco Square Join us for the Congress for the New Urbanism Walking Tour at The Canals at Frisco Square\, a living example of Arcadia Realty's vision for sustainable\, multi-generational\, mixed-use development. Guided by Arcadia principals John Hodge and Bill Gietema along with Robert Acuna-Pilgrim of TBG Partners\, the tour highlights how thoughtful planning creates neighborhoods that welcome people at every stage of life. Experience how a mix of housing types\, inviting open spaces\, senior living options\, and integrated amenities foster a strong and connected community. This is a chance to see how Arcadia and its collaborators translate the principles of New Urbanism into a vibrant\, enduring place. Come walk with us\, explore what makes a great place\, and consider how these ideas can inspire other communities across our region.https://img.evbuc.com/https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.evbuc.com%2Fimages%2F1139222243%2F277497393905%2F1%2Foriginal.20250929-201241?crop=focalpoint&amp\;fit=crop&amp\;h=200&amp\;w=450&amp\;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp\;q=75&amp\;sharp=10&amp\;fp-x=0.527&amp\;fp-y=0.403&amp\;s=5c4f8da2058ee7f7abf1650023a0172b: https://img.evbuc.com/https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.evbuc.com%2Fimages%2F1139222243%2F277497393905%2F1%2Foriginal.20250929-201241?crop=focalpoint&fit=crop&h=200&w=450&auto=format%2Ccompress&q=75&sharp=10&fp-x=0.527&fp-y=0.403&s=5c4f8da2058ee7f7abf1650023a0172b\n\n
LOCATION:https://www.eventbrite.com/e/cnu-walking-tour-canals-at-grand-park-and-frisco-square-tickets-1748110548709
X-ORGANIZING-GROUP:CNU NTX
X-TEAMUP-WHO:CNU NTX
X-EVENT-TYPE:social_gathering
X-REJECTED:false
CREATED:20250930T160404Z
END:VEVENT
