DTSTAMP:20260217T204255Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Chicago:20251029T183000
DTEND;TZID=America/Chicago:20251029T200000
SUMMARY:DBC Marketing Volunteer Meetup
DESCRIPTION:Share your Dallas biking story and help drive the conversation around safe streets in our city!Meet up with DBC marketing volunteers to help create content for social media and the DBC blog. The goal is for each volunteer to be empowered to make one thing before the end of the year - whether it's a video\, photo\, blog\, or some other idea.\n\nExamples:\n- Show us your trip biking to the grocery store\n- biking kids to school\n- dallas social rides\n- safe and unsafe infrastructure\n- taking bikes on DART\n\nVideo\, photography\, and writing skills are extra useful\, but experience is not necessarily required. If you're new and you just want to see what it's all about\, please come and hang out and brainstorm some ideas. No pressure. All are welcome!\nSee more: https://www.facebook.com/share/1HUL4eKCoQ/\n
LOCATION:Westlake Brewing Co: 2816 Commerce St
