SUMMARY:CNU North Texas End of Year Happy Hour (Come join your new urbanist friends as we celebrate a great year in Texas and for our region.)
DESCRIPTION:Who: Come join your new urbanist friends as we celebrate a great year in Texas and for our region.\n\nCome join your new urbanist friends as we celebrate a great year in Texas and for our region.Let's raise a glass to a landmark year for walkable communities in Texas and our region!Join your fellow new urbanist friends to celebrate the significant strides we've made. This year delivered crucial reforms at both state and local levels—hard-won steps toward making our communities more walkable and livable. We also successfully protected and championed mass transit in our region\, a vital victory we must build on. It's time to focus on the successes\, recharge your passion\, and strategize on how we'll accelerate this momentum into 2026. This is your chance to network with the people making change happen. Looking Ahead to 2026 The CNU North Texas chapter is currently planning a variety of engaging events and initiatives. We plan to unveil our 2026 agenda at the Happy Hour\, providing attendees with an early look at the chapter's focus for the upcoming year.Follow @CNUNTX on Instagram and LinkedIn for updates and other informationHappy Hour Details When: Wednesday\, December 3rd\, 6:00 pm to 8:00 pmWhere: The Mucky Duck in the Addison Circle - We will be in the back covered patioTransit Info Closed DART Station is Addison Station (10 Min walk)Bus Routes Along Arapaho Rd.https://img.evbuc.com/https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.evbuc.com%2Fimages%2F1170360363%2F277497393905%2F1%2Foriginal.20251106-222820?crop=focalpoint&amp\;fit=crop&amp\;h=200&amp\;w=450&amp\;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp\;q=75&amp\;sharp=10&amp\;fp-x=0.12&amp\;fp-y=0.419&amp\;s=7c85f7e326003feb1727eeeb0b1c468c: https://img.evbuc.com/https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.evbuc.com%2Fimages%2F1170360363%2F277497393905%2F1%2Foriginal.20251106-222820?crop=focalpoint&fit=crop&h=200&w=450&auto=format%2Ccompress&q=75&sharp=10&fp-x=0.12&fp-y=0.419&s=7c85f7e326003feb1727eeeb0b1c468c\n\n
X-ORGANIZING-GROUP:CNU NTX
X-TEAMUP-WHO:CNU NTX
