SUMMARY:DBC December Coffee (Holiday Hang Out)
DESCRIPTION:Come celebrate all that DBC has accomplished this year! We'll be hanging out at Pull Through from 9-10:30. \n\nArrive by bike or transit: Pull through is right off SOPAC trail or accessible by DART's White Rock Station on the blue line.\n\nOptionally\, join a social ride after coffee led by Friends of the SOPAC trail. The ride will leave at 10:30 from Pull Through. Pace is about 10 mph and go for about an  hour\, so planned to be 8-10 miles long.\nRSVP: https://actionnetwork.org/events/december-coffee-social/\n
