SUMMARY:RBC Cottonwood Advocacy Ride
DESCRIPTION:Join RBC and The Bike Shop on Sunday\, December 14th for an advocacy ride on the Cottonwood Creek Trail. RBC supports Better Block and The Loop Dallas in their mission to activate this trail\, making it more inviting\, inclusive\, and user friendly for all. You can read more information about the ongoing initiative on \nThe Loop's website.\n\n\nRide details:\n\n9:30am - Meet at The Bike Shop around for coffee and treats\n10:00am - Roll out. Route will be approximately 12-15 miles round trip with an option to take the train back to Arapaho station if preferred.\n
LOCATION:The Bike Shop: 1002 N Central Expy Suite 116, Richardson, TX 75080
