DESCRIPTION:Community event\n \nhosted\n \nby\n \nMiso\nWhat started in Wisconsin as an effort to promote winter cycling became known as Santa Cycle Rampage. As participation\, festivities\, and excitement grew\, other cities began adopting their own versions as a way to spread good cheer\, and now we’re on our third year here in Dallas. Proceeds go to a local cyclist in need.\nLocation and more details TBD\, Ride Starts at 1pm. \nStay up to date here.\n
