SUMMARY:Dallas City Council Meetings
DESCRIPTION:Dallas City Council meetings are held every Wednesday at 9am with a break in July and over the holidays. DBC will be organizing opportunities for public comment\, both in person and virtual. Stay up to date with calls to action our our Action Network. \nhttps://actionnetwork.org/groups/dallas-bicycle-coalition\n\nAgenda can found be here: \nhttps://cityofdallas.legistar.com/Calendar.aspx\nLive feed or meeting recordings can be found here: \nhttps://dallastx.new.swagit.com/views/113/city-council\n\nSign up for virtual or in-person public comment: \nhttps://dallascityhall.com/government/citysecretary/Pages/CCrules.aspx\n
LOCATION:Dallas City Hall: 1500 Marilla St, Dallas, TX 75201
