SUMMARY:DBC Second Saturday Coffee Social and Ride
DESCRIPTION:Want to get involved in bike advocacy and make new friends through the bike community? Or looking to explore Dallas on bike? Drop by for DBC's monthly coffee socials and bike ride every second Saturday. \n\nGrab some coffee and hang out from 9-10:30. Get an update on DBC and learn how to get involved. Volunteers to help with the social and ride are needed\, so be sure to mention if you're interested in being a part of our coffee social team! Optionally\, bring your bike and take off on a social paced ride at 10:30. We go about 10mph for an hour before returning back to the starting location. Arriving on bike or transit is highly encouraged\, so leave your car at home if you can.\n\nThe time stays constant\, but locations and community partners rotate around the city. RSVP and find the latest details on our Action Network. \nhttps://actionnetwork.org/groups/dallas-bicycle-coalition\n
LOCATION:Rotates Monthly
