DESCRIPTION:RSVP: https://www.spacydtx.com/list/through-the-backseat-window-benefitting-dart\n\nJoin the Dallas Public Transit Society for Through the Backseat Window\, a film festival supporting public transportation in Dallas\, with screenings of 3 independent films made by filmmakers who use DART not only as a mode of transport\, but also as a vessel for thought. We're holding multiple screenings throughout the day alongside speeches and live music on January 11th from 5pm-9:30pm. RSVP now on the Spacydtx.com website to get your free tickets!!\nExperience the world as you did during childhood\, through the backseat window.
