SUMMARY:Mockingbird Pedestrian Improvements Public Input Meeting (Hosted by TPW)
DESCRIPTION:TPW will host an in-person public meeting to view and discuss designed proposed improvements to the following streets:\n\nMockingbird Lane between U.S. 75 and Greenville Avenue\;\nGreenville Avenue between Mockingbird and Lovers Lane\;\nLovers between U.S. 75 and Greenville\;\nalong the U.S. 75 frontage road between Mockingbird and Lovers.\nThe meeting is scheduled for\n 6 p.m. \non \nWednesday\, Jan. 14\, 2026\,\n at Energy Square One\, 4925 Greenville Ave.\, Room 106. For more information\, email \nmockingbird@piacommunications.com\n.\n\nOther upcoming meetings details tbd:\n- Jupiter Road (TBD)​\n- Malcolm X Boulevard (TBD)​\n\nCheck out the city's public meeting website: \nhttps://dallascityhall.com/departments/transportation/Pages/public-meetings.aspx\n\nPast public meetings: \nhttps://dallascityhall.com/departments/transportation/Pages/past-public-meetings.aspx\n
