SUMMARY:TOD Happy Hour: Deep Ellum Station (Join us for drinks and good vibes at Deep Ellum Station’s TOD Happy Hour—fun times guaranteed!)
DESCRIPTION:Who: Join us for drinks and good vibes at Deep Ellum Station’s TOD Happy Hour—fun times guaranteed!\n\nJoin us for drinks and good vibes at Deep Ellum Station’s TOD Happy Hour—fun times guaranteed!TOD Happy Hour: Deep Ellum Station Join us as we begin a new series of happy hours supporting transit-oriented development! This month\, we head to Deep Ellum Station and visit Backyard Bar\, a dog-friendly bar &amp\; grill with games\, live music\, and delicious food. Whether you're new to the CNU\, public transit\, Deep Ellum\, or a regular to all of it\, all are welcome. Bring a friend! Backyard bar is a 1 minute walk from Deep Ellum Station.https://img.evbuc.com/https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.evbuc.com%2Fimages%2F1175058440%2F277497393905%2F1%2Foriginal.20260116-153533?crop=focalpoint&amp\;fit=crop&amp\;h=200&amp\;w=450&amp\;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp\;q=75&amp\;sharp=10&amp\;fp-x=0.5&amp\;fp-y=0.5&amp\;s=9fd6c1491a278e86c7e9aff27ab70cab: https://img.evbuc.com/https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.evbuc.com%2Fimages%2F1175058440%2F277497393905%2F1%2Foriginal.20260116-153533?crop=focalpoint&fit=crop&h=200&w=450&auto=format%2Ccompress&q=75&sharp=10&fp-x=0.5&fp-y=0.5&s=9fd6c1491a278e86c7e9aff27ab70cab\n\n
