SUMMARY:Transportation and Infrastructure Committee (Dallas City Council)
DESCRIPTION:Transportation and Infrastructure Committee Meeting members were assigned on 8/29/25. They include: Ridley (C)- 14\, Roth (VC)- 11\, Blackmon- 9\, Blair- 8\, Cadena-6\, Gracey-3\, Mendelsohn- 12\n\nMeetings start at 1pm. 2026 Dates (subject to change):\n1/20\, 2/17\, 3/23\, 4/20\, 5/18\, 6/15\, 8/17\, 9/14\, 10/19\, 11/16\,12/8\n\nAgenda can be found here: \nhttps://cityofdallas.legistar.com/Calendar.aspx\nLive feed and meeting recordings found here: \nhttps://dallastx.new.swagit.com/views/113/city-council\n\nStay up to date on calls to action on DBC's Action Network: \nhttps://actionnetwork.org/groups/dallas-bicycle-coalition\n\n
